ol.li: Client-Server Architecture: MAUI app works offline with local SQLite, syncs when online
.NET Aspire Orchestration: Manages backend and Whisper container with service discovery
Background Processing: RecognitionHostedService polls for queued notes and processes them
Speech Recognition: Faster-Whisper container provides OpenAI-compatible API
Data Sync: NoteSyncService handles upload queue and status polling
Local-First: All data stored locally first, then synced to backend
